    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i dont even know why im still typing. everything is gone. the company, the funding, the last three years of my life... just evaporated overnight. the debt is so high i can't even see a way out. i look at my family and i just feel sick. how am i supposed to walk back into my life as this person? i feel like a ghost already.",
